{"tid":405200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李國章：港青不敵內地生　才倡港獨做失敗者","createTime":"2017-09-18T15:56:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T15:25:51.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"118face47f7ac7d5c943d35f358450e3393dc7c5","tid":405200,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170918/large/1505739402_0ec3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170918%2Flarge%2F1505739402_0ec3.png&h=e557bcdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多間大學的民主牆上，近期貼有討論港獨的標語，港大校委會主席李國章認為，本地學生因無法與內地學生競爭，才提倡港獨，形容他們是失敗者心態（mentality of loser）。<br />\n<br />\n李國章接受電視台英文節目訪問，直言港獨思潮「非常簡單」，「因為我們大學裡的年青人不能與內地學生競爭；不論在獎學金、獎項等各方面，內地學生都更優勝（winning all the way）」，故他指年青人拒絕加強競爭、參與「遊戲」，才出現「我不想再跟你玩」、「我們要逃離」、「我們要從你們之中獨立」等說法，稱這些想法「基本上是失敗者的心態（basically the mentality of loser）」。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，李國章認為香港與內地關係非常緊密，食物及食水均來自內地，故討論獨立並無意義，又稱張貼「港獨」標語是違反《基本法》及具煽動性，不屬於學術討論，校方有責任告訴學生對錯，撕去有關標語。<br />\n<br />\n對於立法會議員何君堯及其他團體，早前曾要求港大辭退港大法律系副教授、「佔中」發起人戴耀廷，李國章指會根據校內程序處理，惟稱據他向校長馬斐森查詢所知，「戴教授沒有在課堂上邀請學生參與佔中，所以不能說他違反大學守則」。"},{"pid":"59beb74109feff1ef1f958fc2710d2f4fceec16b","tid":405200,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:57:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170918&amp;guid=57226711&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170918%26guid%3D57226711%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=wca9uF3WYcW0QzuqSMqPTUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=7623d099\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170918%26guid%3D57226711%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=953dffd5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170918&amp;guid=57226711&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"b6e43b2bf441439171086c809d93cdffff71807e","tid":405200,"uid":130513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:02:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d473cb60209f5952b9e46408827db3fd40c6f7cd","tid":405200,"uid":11001,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:02:54.000Z","msg":"[2004-08-01] 李國章：香港無失敗學生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/405047/page/1?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/405047/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7b951639b6a0395ebae2f0d2f06ee7f57909da98","tid":405200,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:05:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28231aa808c7306775cd1476dc9cf81701a34d5b","tid":405200,"uid":83582,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:07:15.000Z","msg":"調轉就岩:<br />\n<br />\n支那學生因無法與香港學生競爭，才反對港獨，形容他們是失敗者心態（mentality of loser）。"},{"pid":"95886d53314cd721dd445bae5e70a9301c0245ae","tid":405200,"uid":34409,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:08:03.000Z","msg":"佢言下之意係咪冇中國留學生就唔會有人講港獨?<br />\n<br />\nlet's do it &hellip;你消滅港獨，立大功啦"},{"pid":"2b1f75f74fe6d5a735029a1747d71367463b02ba","tid":405200,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85558ca96a4806354d71310bd8b40239c56f51ae","tid":405200,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9538a922c5fab3d271b43aa6646edc9ef77b99b2","tid":405200,"uid":5490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T00:13:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/19/081245_e88639eafe58f52abddd6b6c1cdce790.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum