ote><blockquote>佢冇講錯<br />\n要好似佢地家族咁成功，首先要做漢奸走狗，睇死班港青做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"914aebafc1a9627c5d22e2ab36f6bb617aec00d2","tid":405200,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:30:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢冇講錯<br />\n要好似佢地家族咁成功，首先要做漢奸走狗，睇死班港青做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"72c3e437c92e2aef7586b3dea780eae9cd85728c","tid":405200,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪叫啲公司請晒大陸喱囉"},{"pid":"87a843aea40b6e57ab750251e0e85505eb36035d","tid":405200,"uid":53705,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:51:26.000Z","msg":"事實上, 搞革命既人, 從來都係所謂既「失敗者」<br />\n如果不是「失敗者,」又洗乜搞革命, 推翻現有得益者<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n國民黨 全部都是知識份子/有錢人/地主<br />\n中共 都係一班 唔識字既農民/土匪, 屬於「失敗者」, 所以佢地搞革命, 推翻國民黨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有之前烏克蘭革命, 埃及革命.......都是失業率太高<br />\n民眾失業, 無工開, 無飯食, 都是屬於「失敗者」, 所以佢地出來搞革命 ,推翻當權者<br />\n仲有古代果D 黃巢, 李自成 , 洪秀全 都是「失敗者」,所以出來搞革命<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過, 就算佢地係「失敗者」, 都唔緊要<br />\n只要革命成功, 就會變「成功者」<br />\n<br />\n相反, 當權者 被推翻,就會馬上變「失敗者」<br />\n就好似卡達菲, 侯賽因, 要好似老婆咁走佬, 最後比人捉到處決"},{"pid":"4919d3fbe9410f37b01097e05caab6d35542d4cb","tid":405200,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:51:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事實上, 搞革命既人, 從來都係所謂既「失敗者」<br />\n如果不是「失敗者,」又洗乜搞革命, 推翻現有得益者<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n國民黨 全部都是知識份子/有錢人/地主<br />\n中共 都係一班 唔識字既農民/土匪, 屬於「失敗者」, 所以佢地搞革命, 推翻國民黨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有之前烏克蘭革命, 埃及革命.......都是失業率太高<br />\n民眾失業, 無工開, 無飯食, 都是屬於「失敗者」, 所以佢地出來搞革命 ,推翻當權者<br />\n仲有古代果D 黃巢, 李自成 , 洪秀全 都是「失敗者」,所以出來搞革命<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過, 就算佢地係「失敗者」, 都唔緊要<br />\n只要革命成功, 就會變「成功者」<br />\n<br />\n相反, 當權者 被推翻,就會馬上變「失敗者」<br />\n就好似卡達菲, 侯賽因, 要好似<span style=\"color: red;\">老鼠</span>咁走佬, 最後比人捉到處決</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c85faf74c43755f9d8c2fc51e869498dacdaf929","tid":405200,"uid":126590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:32:58.000Z","msg":"駁唔到"},{"pid":"c35c51321cefa1e0272bed961b4c40a1b9885e02","tid":405200,"uid":76470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T14:03:23.000Z","msg":"睇到李國章啲言論覺得自己好一文不值好唔開心，而家好想拎過張投胎卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我無講過講港獨又無搞過咩革命同時又覺得大陸人勁（利申唔係想吹奏大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n點解係要用我地到黎同內地生比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地想廢都難啦,係香港有hall住 要幾時溫書都得何況佢地落黎讀書都唔會有咩娛樂...我地啲香港學生呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一來一回起馬個幾鐘(如果遠嘅話可能唔止添) 有時返到屋企都無晒精神溫書或者要做家務,如果屋企唔係有錢就直頭放學返part time 我想問比黎有咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  根本生活環境都唔同<br />\n<br />\n而家睇完李先生啲言論覺得自己係loser,好無用,直頭係社會垃圾,覺得自己嘅生存價值就係比啲有權有勢嘅人做箭靶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想問下巴打薩瑪莉亞幫唔幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a97d68de0b308b6b0f95ad8e4d5980b207f5094","tid":405200,"uid":60557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T14:08:06.000Z","msg":"點解唔係當權者要反醒下？如果政府係可以令到人民滿意，咁點會有人站岀來。你可以話依家啲青少年競爭力低，睇中大個單就知大學生既英文去到咩程度。但係當民主依啲咁嘅核心價值都要慢慢摧毀，有人覺醒啦，就用失敗者論，你試下係今時今日，你又上唔上到位。社會流動性低，房屋問題，教育問題，成個社會千瘡百孔，點解政府又唔檢討下。港獨唔係「問題」，依家社會發生緊嘅先係「問題」。唔去處理，反而係度話香港既青少年係失敗者，咁既態度係上位者應該有既咩？<br />\nSor for 1999"},{"pid":"940d07d5b48dfeac60fafd5bbea744122212af29","tid":405200,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T10:44:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢冇講錯<br />\n要好似佢地家族咁成功，首先要做漢奸走狗，睇死班港青做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f453011c93a6877f5f8156ca9991d0e2d38c8a62","tid":405200,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T15:51:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢冇講錯<br />\n要好似佢地家族咁成功，首先要做漢奸走狗，睇死班港青做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2913595aac3c5e88bb5f3307b9484e7a5fcf17fc","tid":405200,"uid":5419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T16:32:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢冇講錯<br />\n要好似佢地家族咁成功，首先要做漢奸走狗，睇死班港青做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj